Abstract = {In the past decades, Information technology has been a topic for
   frequent graduate research theses. Today, CAD technology has been widely
   used in several architecture fields. Several CAD applications for the
   architecture practice go beyond the graphic software, such as rapid
   prototyping, parametric design, generative systems, etc. The purpose of
   this research is to survey and categorize academic graduate theses that
   have been produced in architecture schools, in Brazil and abroad, within
