   Int Assoc Struct \& Architecture},
Abstract = {Since 2010, the School of Architecture of the University of A Coruna
   (ETSAC) has implemented the use of parametric tools for the study and
   analysis of building structures. Students in the subject of ``Structural
   Design{''}, located in the fifth year of the degree entitled to exercise
