   intensively throughout the course with open source applications of
   parametric analysis. The students acquire throughout the course the
   competences and skills necessary to carry out the strategies for
   generating the analytical structural model of different tensegrity and
   reciprocal structures. The availability in ETSAC FABLAB of digital
