Volume = {31},
Number = {1},
Pages = {104-112},
Month = {JAN 5},
Abstract = {For product packaging, the visual elements in it can further enhance the
   appeal of the package to customers. This article briefly introduces
   visual elements and packaging design and made an example analysis with
   the gift packaging design of Squirrel Design Studio. In the case study,
   the packaging design of the studio's mirror, storage bag, and puzzle was
   rated by hierarchical analysis and questionnaires, and the packaging
   design was analyzed based on the rating results. A convolutional neural
   network (CNN) was also used to evaluate packages in batches. The results
   showed that the CNN could make a batch evaluation of gift packaging
   design accurately; the three gift packaging designs were based on the
   studio's logo, making the ratings similar; in addition, the packaging
   design patterns were composed of different geometric shapes to show the
   studio's innovative design theme, and the squirrel silhouette and text
   description were used to strengthen the impression of the studio among
   customers.},
